      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Amos 8:9",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " literally fulfilled: and the vail of the temple was rent in the midst. The Persic version renders it, \"the gate of the temple\"; and so the Syriac version, \"the face of the gate of the temple\"; See Gill on ",
